Okhulumela uMnyango weMfundo ePhakeme kuzwelonke uMnuz Madikwe Mabotha, uthe kumele abafundi bakwamukele ukuthi akusibo bonke abazokwamukelwa enyuvesi. Uthi;* Enyuvesi akungeni noma ngubani, kumele ube uphase ngendlela edingwa yileyo nyuvesi.* Kulabo abangathathwanga emanyuvesi akhona amakolishi amaTechnical and Vocational Education Training (TVET), anezikhala ezilinganiswa ku-100 000 kuzwelonke.* Sinalo nohlelo lokuqeqesha abafundi emisebenzini yezandla efana neMotor Mechanic, Artisan Development Centre okuvuleleke kubafundi abaphase ngo-50% kuya phezulu kwiPhysical Science.Abafundi basengafaka izicelo ngokuthumela imiphumela yabo ku: [email&#160;protected]* Kumele bangenzeli ukubukwa ukuthi bafunda enyuvesi kepha babhekisise kahle ukuthi bazowuthola yini umsebenzi lapho beqeda izifundo zabo.* Imisebenzi yezandla isiyakhokhela nayo manje, abafundi mabangayibukeli phansi.